-- Explosion Injured a Swiss Embassy Official in Rome, Italy Police Say
-- B y   T o m m a s o   E b h a r d t
-- 2010-12-23T11:39:17Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-12-23/explosion-injured-a-swiss-embassy-official-in-rome-italy-police-say.html
 An  explosion injured a Swiss
Embassy official in Rome today, a police spokesman said by
phone.  “We have no information at the moment, as we have just
received the reports and we are still trying to establish
the facts,” said Charlotte Huwiler from the Swiss foreign
ministry media office.  Calls and emails to the Swiss embassy in Rome weren’t
immediately returned.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Tommaso Ebhardt at 
 tebhardt@bloomberg.net  